<db:section xml:id="updateAxesContinuously-prop">
<db:title>[since 5.15] updateAxesContinuously : bool</db:title>
<db:fieldsynopsis>
<db:modifier>(Qt property)</db:modifier>
<db:type>bool</db:type>
<db:varname>updateAxesContinuously</db:varname>
<db:synopsisinfo role="access">public</db:synopsisinfo>
<db:synopsisinfo role="status">active</db:synopsisinfo>
<db:synopsisinfo role="threadsafeness">unspecified</db:synopsisinfo>
<db:synopsisinfo role="getter">updateAxesContinuously</db:synopsisinfo>
<db:synopsisinfo role="setter">setUpdateAxesContinuously</db:synopsisinfo>
<db:synopsisinfo role="notifier">updateAxesContinuouslyChanged</db:synopsisinfo>
</db:fieldsynopsis>
<db:para>If <db:code>true</db:code>, axes will be updated anytime they change regardless of whether any mouse button is being pressed. Otherwise, axes are updated only when one of the mouse buttons is being pressed.</db:para>
<db:para>The default value is <db:code>false</db:code>.</db:para>
<db:para>This property was introduced in Qt 5.15.</db:para>
